{"tid":897804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蝗蟲東涌遊--飯後免費節目：跟「領隊」去「爬山」，幾乎所有團友會跟隨。","createTime":"2018-11-11T08:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T08:37:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c16e11baf5f6bde659652330ec94e1b480ee68","tid":897804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2079170/org/7e0b69b206ff0f14b081aef787fa3fe7.jpg/8x_kfBbsAwWoKxFzYjwgpliXAdwswHlLkR1HcpEdR3I?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2079170%2Forg%2F7e0b69b206ff0f14b081aef787fa3fe7.jpg%2F8x_kfBbsAwWoKxFzYjwgpliXAdwswHlLkR1HcpEdR3I%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=91fd78c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自廣州的劉小姐表示，從微信群得知有港珠澳一日自由行，遂今早從廣州出發到珠海，再乘車經港珠澳大橋來港，事前只需付車費。她說，內地「領隊」帶團友來港，會安排行程讓團友自由參與，下午自行用膳後便隨「領隊」去「爬山」，不用額外付款，故幾乎所有團友會跟隨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/257694/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%B9%A7%E5%88%B0%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E8%90%AC%E5%AF%A7%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%96%E9%A3%9F%E9%9B%9E%E9%AB%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F257694%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%259B%259E%25E9%25AB%2580&d=v4F1GY0%2Bs36xT1iXQeKYI10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=65d2d404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/257694/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E5%9C%98%E7%B9